<p>The state's commitment to renewable energy, coupled with stable utility rates and excellent solar resource availability, positions Missouri homeowners to capitalize on long-term energy savings. With net metering policies in place and property tax exemptions for solar installations, the financial benefits extend well beyond monthly utility bill reductions, making solar and HVAC investments some of the most cost-effective home improvements available in the Show-Me State.</p>

